Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即向荆州用兵 攻伐刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父相 此时荆襄正是多雨季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕不利于骑兵作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是否等到 雨 雨季过后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我儿长进了 知道天时地利了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 荆襄雨季即将结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而我们从许昌进军到荆襄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}需要五天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等我们的人马到荆襄的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但雨季已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就连地面也已经风干了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丝毫无碍战马奔驰 你说对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲说得是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 我忽略了进军的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁听令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}命你为主将
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}李典为副将
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}率精兵五万进驻樊城
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虎视荆襄各郡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待我令下 则攻取新野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将领命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们这就去整军待命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.55,0:01:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}李典
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道你处事谨慎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以才派你给曹仁做副将
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁 虽勇 但他性急
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立功心切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必要时 你要劝他妥当用兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备兵虽少 却是劲敌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们屯兵樊城后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要观其虚实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再择动兵时机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 前面就是樊城了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令城守开门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说上将军曹仁到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军曹仁到 快开城门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 我们进城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你领军进城休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我亲领数骑 到新野探查一番
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听说 新野距此八十余里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}探营可派哨骑前去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何劳将军亲往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大战已迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为将者 应当知已知彼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相让我们屯军樊城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待命出击呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听将军的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仿佛即刻就要出战了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你传令各部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日让他们好生休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日五更出发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随我踏平新野 生擒刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军不可轻敌呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们还是等候丞相的军令到时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再进军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看你是害怕刘关张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不怕刘关张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却也不轻视刘关张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日 我给你五千军马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你守城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我自去取新野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军不可呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}李典 你妒嫉我独建大功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将绝无此意呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你为何违杭我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下奉命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 曹军到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军曹仁已在关前布下战阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}声声挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹军来得好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师还说三十日兵到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前后差不过两天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在足足差了三天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只差一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师已经是料敌如神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟莫要强辩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雨季未止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操已经向新野用兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在他进军途中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雨季结束 地面也干了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操不凡哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁也能布出这等阵法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人有上将军之才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}屠猪贩酒之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}识得曹仁将军阵法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快快出城迎阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则攻破城池 鸡犬不留
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 令将士坚守不战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只用弓弩射住两翼即可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待正午过后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敌势稍弱 我再设法破敌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙 快去布置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师根本不识曹仁的阵法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他自个怯敌不说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不让咱们去杀敌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊 暑气正盛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们且回去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鼠辈 快快出城迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}缩头乌龟 快快出城迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹军所驻的樊城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乃是一座五百多年的古城了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下曾经登城观景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到城楼西角处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长着一丛蒲扇大的灵芝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黑里透红 极为珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难得 难得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连年兵火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不知那灵芝焚毁了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 如果在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早晚取来泡茶 那可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师 茶喝够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都正午了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}破敌之策想出来了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁引阵 名叫八门金锁阵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:08:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}休 生 伤 杜 景 死 惊 开八门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此阵本是孙膑所创古阵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}经历代兵家发展 已有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阵中这座将台 名叫龙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是后来所创
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 曹仁只学得阵形阵法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却没有学得精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只需一员猛将带五百精甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从东南生门杀入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从正西景门杀出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此阵必破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听说你一颗铁胆 七尺长枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出入万军丛中有如观鱼赏花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就请你辛苦一趟如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将领命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐庶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是故意气俺张翼德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂敢 待赵将军破阵后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张将军与关将军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就可以随主公大举杀入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来人哪 在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}取我战甲来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弟兄们 敌将挑战 变阵迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}破阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎敌 不要乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我顶住 顶住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要乱 不要乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要乱 不要乱 稳住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弟兄们 稳住 迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顶住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快撤 快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 伤势重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不碍事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}李典啊 你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此战我轻敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到刘备手下有能人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然破了我的八门金锁阵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下建议
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}退军驻守樊城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立刻遣人将敌情报给丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待丞相的大军到后 再取新野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这新野弹丸之地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何劳丞相亲征啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此外 今日的败讯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也不必禀报丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待我今夜攻下新野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你再一并禀报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军你想夜袭新野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备刚刚胜利一场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他肯定是兴高采烈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他见我军兵败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必然以为我不敢再轻举妄动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是我偏要出其所料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夜袭新野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵法云
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出其不意 攻其无防
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是指此时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 不可轻敌呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备身边如有高人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那他定有防备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军不能一误再误啦 李典
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这么胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还打什么仗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你如果害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:17:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是留守吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我自领军前去 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军如果非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下也当领一支兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用以接应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成 我分你五千军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}距我二十里跟进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以防不测
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们那是什么破八门金锁阵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被子龙的铁骑一冲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在全成了破瓜烂枣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹军伤亡足足两千人马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再加上关将军这么一射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁掉下台来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差点性命不保啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来曹军 也是不堪一击呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过如此啊 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 曹仁虽然折了一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但并没有完败
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下来我们该当如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我料曹仁今夜必来劫营
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这也是曹操惯用的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}败而不退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反而出其不意 再次进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁平生就喜欢效仿曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只可惜他学曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就像学八阵法一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只学了个皮毛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁兵锋所向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我们城外的大营
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们应当在曹仁进军的半路上伏击他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}樊城与新野之间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一片山洼 名叫蛇口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张飞 赵云
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着你们领一万军马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}埋伏于蛇口前后两端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待曹仁军到 放他进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待他军过其半
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你俩再分头杀出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫曹军首尾难顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必然大获全胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师 那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关将军辛苦些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去樊城采灵芝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁大军既出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}樊城必然空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着你带八千兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直取樊城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顺便把城楼那朵灵芝采回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给主公泡茶喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然 如果它还在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弟兄们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加速前进 穿出山口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}点火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快撤 快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快撤 快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军在此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快开城门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:22:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师有令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫我不必杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则 你只有葬身在这城下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽 你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是我对手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回许昌叫曹操来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公 军师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张 赵两位将军在蛇口大胜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}歼敌两万 俘获战马兵器无数
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公 军师 曹仁已逃回许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所率残兵不到百骑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:23:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公 军师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关将军已取下樊城
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}城中有曹军军粮二十万石
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}钱十万 全部归于我军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.08,0:24:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你手里捧的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.78,0:24:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}取樊城后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.71,0:24:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关将军亲自登上城楼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又亲手采下这朵灵芝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.92,0:24:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}献予主公 军师泡茶喝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.24,0:24:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.94,0:24:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这灵芝乃百草之圣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.58,0:24:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你便是人中之圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.89,0:24:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.46,0:24:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公此话 在下万万不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.31,0:25:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.68,0:25:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备起兵二十余年
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.62,0:25:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}屡战屡败
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.75,0:25:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从来没有过像今天这样的大胜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.99,0:25:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且战胜的是曹军主将
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.66,0:25:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生你不但带给了我胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更带给了我信心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.54,0:25:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}除曹贼 兴汉室
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.94,0:25:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.19,0:26:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.73,0:26:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁大败而归 樊城也给丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.77,0:26:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他把自己捆起来 跪在府外
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.87,0:26:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等候丞相治罪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.34,0:26:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}李典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.64,0:26:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}同跪待罪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.45,0:26:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫李典进来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.68,0:26:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.72,0:26:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给李典松绑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.79,0:26:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.23,0:26:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罪将李典 拜见丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.67,0:26:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为你处事谨慎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.21,0:26:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才叫你辅助曹仁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.24,0:26:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁轻敌冒进
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.85,0:26:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你为何不阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.78,0:27:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将曾经再三地劝阻
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.02,0:27:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是 劝不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.26,0:27:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请丞相治罪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.39,0:27:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胜败乃兵家常事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.50,0:27:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}损几万兵 丢个城池
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.80,0:27:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.93,0:27:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没料到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.00,0:27:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备居然能够识破我的金锁阵法
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.34,0:27:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.64,0:27:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}破金锁八门阵的不是刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.28,0:27:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是他新拜的军师
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.28,0:27:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}名叫徐庶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.98,0:27:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐庶是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.29,0:27:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 此人我认识
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.19,0:27:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他叫徐元直
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.16,0:27:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}襄阳名士 精通兵法 深明韬略
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.27,0:27:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他的才华 比你如何
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.17,0:27:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胜我数倍
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.67,0:27:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.07,0:27:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}数倍乃至数十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.48,0:28:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备过去只有
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.85,0:28:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张飞 关羽等武将
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.85,0:28:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在又添了个军师
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.89,0:28:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂不是要龙生双翼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.33,0:28:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天哪 母亲哪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.53,0:28:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿不孝 累你受罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.11,0:28:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.51,0:28:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.41,0:28:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.11,0:28:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我小弟徐康去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.25,0:28:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母年已年过六旬 无人供养
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.99,0:28:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只好出门乞讨
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.59,0:28:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事被曹操知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.56,0:28:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操派人把我母亲抓进了许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.69,0:28:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下了大牢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.19,0:28:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.29,0:28:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是我母亲在牢里的手书
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.73,0:28:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说我如不归降曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.83,0:28:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操就要把我母亲架到火炉上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.20,0:28:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}活生生烤死
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.30,0:29:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恕我无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.17,0:29:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要前往许昌 以身赎母
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.54,0:29:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.78,0:29:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生且慢 曹操虽然奸恶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.75,0:29:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我想他断断不能
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.18,0:29:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把六旬老人架在火上生生烤死
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.49,0:29:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请先生安心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.55,0:29:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}容我设法相救 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.06,0:29:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.29,0:29:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要去许昌 现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.16,0:29:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早到一刻是一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.63,0:29:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不能让老母在牢里受罪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.56,0:29:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.63,0:29:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 这也许是曹操的奸计呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.81,0:29:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 这事我想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.31,0:29:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪怕是曹操的奸计
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.71,0:29:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.28,0:29:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老母居于北方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.75,0:29:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而冀州早就归于了北方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.35,0:29:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操如想拿我母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.45,0:29:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那简直是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.22,0:29:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 容我告辞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.60,0:30:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.77,0:30:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我身为人子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.37,0:30:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母亲有难 岂能坐视
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.44,0:30:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此外 我心神已乱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.25,0:30:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已不能辅佐主公了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.85,0:30:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.75,0:30:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这一切都是天意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.89,0:30:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 容我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.94,0:30:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.68,0:30:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.35,0:30:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}备马
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.21,0:30:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.56,0:31:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.66,0:31:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}送君千里 终有一别
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.53,0:31:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.40,0:31:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}君此去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.74,0:31:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.28,0:31:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知何年何月才能相见
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.08,0:31:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与主公相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.42,0:31:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我平生一大快事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.49,0:31:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不幸中途而别
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.03,0:31:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公放心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.40,0:31:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我到许昌之后
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.54,0:31:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}终生不为曹操拟一谋 设一计
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.74,0:31:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只求侍奉母亲 以尽天年
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.98,0:32:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保重 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.95,0:32:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜别主公
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.88,0:32:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听令
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.01,0:32:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.65,0:32:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天把前面那片树林全部伐尽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.05,0:32:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.82,0:32:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何要 要砍掉那片树林
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.56,0:32:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}它挡住了徐元直的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.63,0:32:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.26,0:32:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.55,0:33:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.61,0:33:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 你不走了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.95,0:33:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.05,0:33:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.29,0:33:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因我心乱如麻
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.89,0:33:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然忘了件天大的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.19,0:33:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.83,0:33:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}襄阳城外三十里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.10,0:33:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一片山野 名叫隆中
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.27,0:33:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}住着一位当代奇才
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.60,0:33:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公如果得到他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.47,0:33:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无异于周公得吕望
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.37,0:33:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汉王得张良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.31,0:33:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人才华比君如何
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.88,0:33:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿我比他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.65,0:33:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那真是弩马比麒麟
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.22,0:33:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}寒鸦比凤凰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.36,0:33:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人有经天纬地之才
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.69,0:33:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}堪称天下第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.49,0:33:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当真
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.69,0:33:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.13,0:33:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人姓诸葛 字孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.20,0:34:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为住于卧龙冈上
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.14,0:34:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以又号卧龙先生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.04,0:34:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卧龙
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.24,0:34:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多年来 他身边的师朋们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.98,0:34:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}纷纷各寻其主
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.98,0:34:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}或事曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.05,0:34:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}或事袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.22,0:34:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}或事公孙瓒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.92,0:34:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以便成就功名大业
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.55,0:34:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唯有孔明独居山野
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.02,0:34:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}栖身草棚 巍然不动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.86,0:34:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他为何这样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.46,0:34:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也曾问过孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.80,0:34:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你因何如此
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.10,0:34:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孔明笑道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操 袁绍 公孙瓒之流
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.87,0:34:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不配做他的主公
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.27,0:34:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我再问他
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.68,0:34:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么天下谁配做你的主公
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.48,0:34:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孔明叹道 只怕没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.92,0:34:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与其寻找主公
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.52,0:34:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如为自己创造一个主公
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.42,0:34:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与其寻找主公
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.59,0:35:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如自己创造一个主公
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.36,0:35:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这话说得空前绝后 千古未闻
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.44,0:35:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想不到这世间
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.17,0:35:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然真有此等大贤
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.84,0:35:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此前我不说此人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.71,0:35:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是因为我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.41,0:35:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他胸怀云霄之志
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.11,0:35:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只怕不愿意投效主公
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.15,0:35:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢先生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.82,0:35:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备就算肝脑涂地
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.89,0:35:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也一定会请得孔明出山
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.99,0:35:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉 难哪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.13,0:35:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但愿主公 有此幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.60,0:35:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜别
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.77,0:35:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.70,0:36:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与其寻找主公
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.11,0:36:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如为自己创造一个主公
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.64,0:36:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪怕我肝脑涂地
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.38,0:37:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也要求得孔明出山
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.09,0:37:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请问来者可是徐元直吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.02,0:37:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不错 在下正是徐庶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.29,0:37:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请问阁下是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.59,0:37:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就是被先生打败的上将军
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.56,0:37:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.07,0:37:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因在下损兵折将
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.67,0:37:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公罚我在此迎候先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.14,0:37:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在这儿已经是站了三天三夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.84,0:37:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要是再不来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.14,0:37:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的腿 可就要站断了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.71,0:37:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹将军
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.88,0:37:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请将军带我去见丞相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.75,0:37:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请 请 请
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.66,0:37:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}元直
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.46,0:37:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待罪之徒徐庶 拜见丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.30,0:37:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}元直啊 我对你真是朝思暮想
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.14,0:37:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问丞相 家母在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.31,0:38:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令堂大人 正在客馆歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.58,0:38:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家母没在牢里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.41,0:38:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是谁人给我曹操造的谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.68,0:38:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生的母亲就如同我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.22,0:38:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎么会把自个儿的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.92,0:38:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关进牢狱里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.26,0:38:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.49,0:38:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她老人家正在客馆里歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.09,0:38:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.29,0:38:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}容我见过母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.36,0:38:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再来拜谢丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.40,0:38:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 请
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.60,0:38:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快去快回 我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.34,0:38:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}娘 娘
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.98,0:38:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.78,0:38:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}娘
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.62,0:38:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿啊 是你吗 真的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.62,0:38:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}娘 儿来迟了 让母亲受罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.56,0:38:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庶儿 你来了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.53,0:38:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你来了就好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.27,0:38:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}娘想你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.80,0:39:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}娘在梦里都惦记着你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.05,0:39:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.95,0:39:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是在刘皇叔那儿效力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.19,0:39:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何来许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.29,0:39:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}娘 儿接到一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.72,0:39:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说母亲被曹操抓入牢中
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.96,0:39:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要儿来许昌 以身相赎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.00,0:39:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为娘从来就不曾写过什么信
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.57,0:39:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是奸计
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.97,0:39:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 你难道看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.71,0:39:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.14,0:39:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是 儿不能不来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.11,0:39:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.38,0:39:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿身为人子
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.45,0:39:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母亲被囚 儿岂能不来相救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.52,0:39:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庶儿啊 庶儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.99,0:39:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 你从小饱读诗书
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.16,0:40:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不会不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.86,0:40:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这自古忠孝难两全哪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.27,0:40:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘皇叔乃仁义之君 贤德之至
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.74,0:40:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}名满天下呀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.04,0:40:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他又是皇室宗亲
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.45,0:40:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你能够为他效命
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.88,0:40:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是为大汉尽忠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.72,0:40:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.42,0:40:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他 他是欺君罔上的奸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.76,0:40:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐庶啊 徐庶
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.63,0:40:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为娘万万想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.67,0:40:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你竟会弃明投暗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.84,0:40:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成了个愚夫蠢汉哪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.78,0:40:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}娘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.46,0:41:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐庶虽生犹死
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.43,0:41:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他终生不为曹操献一策 出一谋
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.90,0:41:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由此 不好啦 不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.27,0:41:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐庶入曹营 老人家悬梁自尽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.91,0:41:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一言不发 娘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.17,0:41:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成为千古名典
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.04,0:41:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}娘
